    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a glass-like finish, and the interior is immaculate, showing no signs of wear or use. It has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally maintained, with a complete service history to verify its mechanical perfection. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a truly showroom-quality example that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
